{"tid":2463031,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"10年過去，那個賣腎買手機的少年終於發聲了，原來讀書才是最好走的路","createTime":"2021-03-26T11:33:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-27T05:02:22.000Z","uid":1086,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"cf34d9d509a99bef5abd45b63d2846aa9d7e21e2","tid":2463031,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T11:33:33.000Z","msg":"提起&ldquo;賣腎換手機&rdquo;這個梗，許多人都一笑置之，卻鮮有人知，這個梗的背後，包含了一個少年無盡痛苦和懊悔的一生。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p9.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20210224/407d3c772e244d389b14d775365c8681.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp9.itc.cn%2Fq_70%2Fimages03%2F20210224%2F407d3c772e244d389b14d775365c8681.jpeg&h=84a47302&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n儘管它的昂貴讓普通人難以高攀，但仍有許多人趨之若鶩。只因在一些人看來，能夠手握蘋果手機，在夥伴面前亮相，是一件很時髦，甚至稱得上炫酷的事。<br />\n<br />\n那一年，來自安徽的小王17歲，正在上高中，1.9米高的個子，意氣風發，人生可期。<br />\n他也被當時的&ldquo;蘋果熱&rdquo;浪潮裹挾著，幻想著有一部蘋果手機，可以在同學面前炫耀。<br />\n無奈的是，家境拮据，滿足不了他這個慾望。<br />\n在虛榮心的驅使下，他摸索起旁門左道。<br />\n恰逢其時，網上出現了賣腎的中介信息。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>賣一個腎可以給2萬塊！</strong><br />\n<br />\n被貪婪纏繞的他，萌生了可怕的想法：&ldquo;一個腎臟對我來說足夠了，為什麼需要另一個？為什麼不賣它？&rdquo;<br />\n賣了腎，錢就有了。<br />\n<br />\n那時的他，並不知道自己這一個不以為然的決定，會令他從此改變一生。<br />\n懷揣著&ldquo;賣腎求榮&rdquo;美夢的他，被中介帶去郴州，進行了一場9小時的手術，用右腎換來了2.2萬元。<br />\n回來後，他如願以償地用這筆錢用了一部iPhone4，還有一台iPad。<br />\n一頭扎進了歡喜中的他，無心學業，終日沈迷遊戲，還天真地偷樂，以為自己做了划算的買賣。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><p class=\"center\">卻不知前路漫漫，等候他的是多少的痛苦和煎熬！</p></strong><br />\n<br />\n正如在斯蒂芬&middot;茨威格的《斷頭王后》裡說的，&ldquo;命運饋贈的禮物，早已在暗中標好了價格。 &rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n慢慢地，他的身體出現了異樣。<br />\n<br />\n總是無精打采，昏昏欲睡，甚至臥床不起。<br />\n父母終於察覺了問題，追問之下，才得知真相。<br />\n給他做摘腎手術的黑診所，環境惡劣，導致傷口感染。術後也未得到很好的護理，從而導致身體損毀嚴重。<br />\n餘下的左腎，功能嚴重受損，已是3級傷殘。<br />\n如今，10年過去，1.9米的高小伙，只有120斤，沒有學歷，無法工作，終日癱臥在床，需要終身服藥。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p4.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20210224/fb850a2414b74ccc9641b79427adf4d4.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp4.itc.cn%2Fq_70%2Fimages03%2F20210224%2Ffb850a2414b74ccc9641b79427adf4d4.jpeg&h=63450591&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n小王的母親痛苦地說：&ldquo;病情控制得不好，可能會得尿毒症，甚至要換腎。&rdquo;<br />\n重病纏身的他，學業無法繼續，工作更談不上。<br />\n明明正是大好年華，餘生卻已一眼到頭，空留無限悔恨。<br />\n偉大的投資人查理&middot;芒格說過：&ldquo;要得到你想要的東西，最可靠的方法就是讓自己配得上它。 &rdquo;<br />\n作為父母，我們應該要引導孩子明白，窮從來不丟人，任由自己淪為慾望的奴隸才丟人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20210224/809fc2d71f264db893c189a67aa0c8a0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.itc.cn%2Fq_70%2Fimages03%2F20210224%2F809fc2d71f264db893c189a67aa0c8a0.png&h=4551c64b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ee886774bf0874437bce803dea101e8fc91072af","tid":2463031,"uid":73241,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T11:36:44.000Z","msg":"on9仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba6b45e8b50a30988f86f7421d12eb3d8292eb6b","tid":2463031,"uid":157138,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T12:54:13.000Z","msg":"橫掂都成世做廢人，不如賣晒其他器官佢啦，幫你老豆老母換部iphone都好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d82415a9364a2181f35696c69a4dfc7d50d33679","tid":2463031,"uid":248493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T13:06:02.000Z","msg":"肯攞嗰2萬買必乾咪得囉！仲未遲！"},{"pid":"62948ec853d81cc3d3e794a1e84f89d6df82d7c3","tid":2463031,"uid":109629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T13:10:43.000Z","msg":"男人無左個腎係咪會無力屌閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4982091d7744e31eb7f7dc51ba04144773fc3d02","tid":2463031,"uid":12884,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T13:14:10.000Z","msg":"呢個故事嘅教訓係賣完腎要好好護理"},{"pid":"0e4900071ef791e24990226509af888217ce294c","tid":2463031,"uid":66242,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4982091d7744e31eb7f7dc51ba04144773fc3d02","tid":2463031,"uid":12884,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T13:14:10.000Z","msg":"呢個故事嘅教訓係賣完腎要好好護理"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T13:19:24.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n呢篇文章個作者寫得衰<br />\n層次好低"},{"pid":"c93f10b00adb37acd4c3a75f66ac43d44e90156e","tid":2463031,"uid":49119,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T13:24:44.000Z","msg":"10年後先講埋d廢話<br />\n<br />\n咁我都識講，真正玩法係10年前賣賢20k all in bitcoin，ok?"},{"pid":"032570dcc9128ace5544e8e9b79128fc3cc69bb2","tid":2463031,"uid":379746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T13:30:17.000Z","msg":"賣腎成功幫助6億人脫貧<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6ac1893ba31f668431313a8c6bbeefcb9b6e2bd","tid":2463031,"uid":2746,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T15:42:13.000Z","msg":"賣完真係收足錢，實屬難能可貴<br />\n絕對公平買賣守信行為<br />\n只怪青年不懂自己護理傷口<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27ef08d42464e8f6add99d70a95b50a63ebe8d84","tid":2463031,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T15:45:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://storage.cloudconvert.com/tasks/7cf9752e-bbd7-43bb-b97d-27128b981d37/LIHKG--fbdown.net.gif?AWSAccessKeyId=cloudconvert-production&amp;Expires=1616859201&amp;Signature=mqNZlTRh1gVe65GRYXlXnO5khsE%3D&amp;response-content-disposition=attachment%3B%20filename%3D%22LIHKG--fbdown.net.gif%22&amp;response-content-type=image%2Fgif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.cloudconvert.com%2Ftasks%2F7cf9752e-bbd7-43bb-b97d-27128b981d37%2FLIHKG--fbdown.net.gif%3FAWSAccessKeyId%3Dcloudconvert-production%26Expires%3D1616859201%26Signature%3DmqNZlTRh1gVe65GRYXlXnO5khsE%253D%26response-content-disposition%3Dattachment%253B%2520filename%253D%2522LIHKG--fbdown.net.gif%2522%26response-content-type%3Dimage%252Fgif&h=8b8d9879&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1cfdb88f8a460fd1dbeb9d0df4fad4f1e18022ae","tid":2463031,"uid":1